<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Order Has Shipped - AutoXpress</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .shipping-details {
      background: #f0f9ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
    }
    .tracking-info {
      background: #fef3c7;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .tracking-number {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #dc2626;
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .status-badge {
      background: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">üì¶ AutoXpress</div>
      <h2>Your Order Has Shipped!</h2>
      <p>Order #<%= @order.order_number %></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Great news, <%= @customer.name %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Your AutoXpress order is on its way! We've carefully packaged your <strong><%= @order.product_name %></strong> and handed it off to our shipping partner.</p>
      
      <% if @dispatch&.tracking_number.present? %>
        <div class="tracking-info">
          <h3>üìç Track Your Package</h3>
          <p>Tracking Number:</p>
          <div class="tracking-number"><%= @dispatch.tracking_number %></div>
          <% if @dispatch.tracking_link.present? %>
            <a href="<%= @dispatch.tracking_link %>" class="button">Track Your Package</a>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div class="tracking-info" style="background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;">
          <h3>üì¶ Package Preparation</h3>
          <p>Your order has been processed and is being prepared for shipment. You'll receive tracking information within the next 24 hours.</p>
          <p><strong>We'll email you again</strong> as soon as tracking details are available!</p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      
      <div class="shipping-details">
        <h4>üìã Shipping Details</h4>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Order Number:</span>
          <span><strong>#<%= @order.order_number %></strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Product:</span>
          <span><%= @order.product_name %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Vehicle:</span>
          <span><%= @order.car_year %> <%= @order.car_make_model %></span>
        </div>
        <% if @dispatch %>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Shipping Status:</span>
            <span><span class="status-badge"><%= @dispatch.shipment_status.humanize %></span></span>
          </div>
          <% if @dispatch.shipment_status == 'in_transit' %>
            <div class="detail-row">
              <span>Estimated Delivery:</span>
              <span><%= @order.estimated_delivery&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") || "2-3 business days" %></span>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Shipping Address:</span>
          <span><%= @order.customer_address %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>üöö What to Expect:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>In Transit:</strong> Your package is on the way to you</li>
        <li><strong>Delivery:</strong> Watch for delivery updates via tracking</li>
        <li><strong>Installation:</strong> Professional installation available upon request</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>üí° Installation Tips:</strong></p>
      <p>Need help installing your <%= @order.product_name %>? We recommend consulting with a qualified mechanic or our technical support team at <strong>(555) 123-AUTO</strong>.</p>
      
      <p>Questions about your shipment? Reply to this email or call us!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>AutoXpress</strong> - Premium Automotive Parts</p>
      <p>This email was sent regarding order #<%= @order.order_number %></p>
      <p>¬© <%= Date.current.year %> AutoXpress. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>